snippet.title: Def Jam Vendetta Trailer
snippet.description:
This trailer was ripped from the Demo Disc of Issue 14 from Playstation 2 Official Magazine Australia.

This trailer is for Def Jam Vendetta

Notes from Uploader:
This was back when Ludacris was a good musician.
The game looks like a decent wrestling game.
The Def Jam games were pretty good for their time when it comes to fighting games, so i don't find this one disappointing. Again, this was back when EA didn't suck.
